          <div class="tool-review-cons">
            <h3>Cons</h3>
            <ul class="cons-list">
              <li>Ultimate edition is expensive ($149/year for individuals)</li>
              <li>Resource-heavy, requires 8GB+ RAM for comfort</li>
              <li>Slower startup compared to lightweight editors</li>
